OL,3,CCouncil tax in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,4,Cto increase by 8.5%
OL,6,FIt is also increasing fees and charges
OL,7,Fof council services such as at council-
OL,8,Frun leisure facilities and waste
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FCouncil leaders say that they were
OL,12,Ffacing a funding gap of #34.8million
OL,13,Fover the next three years due to
OL,14,Finflation, the rise in pay settlements
OL,15,Fand an increased demand for social
OL,16,Fcare.
OL,18,FThey say they will make savings of
OL,19,Fmore than #4million this year rising
OL,20,Fto nearly #10million by 2029.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
