PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772467873
OL,3,CCouncil tax in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,4,Cto increase by 8.5%
OL,6,FMoney has been found for the
OL,7,FWhitesands Flood Scheme which got the
OL,8,Fgreen light in December last year.
OL,10,FThere will also be capital funding for
OL,11,Fthe Newton Stewart Flood Protection
OL,12,FScheme, the Dumfries Academy/Loreburn
OL,13,FPrimary school campus project,
OL,14,Fimprovements to the Thistle Grove
OL,15,Ftravellers' site and initiatives
OL,16,Fwithin the Borderlands Growth Deal.
OL,18,FDumfries and Galloway Council
OL,19,FConvener, Councillor Katie Hagmann,
OL,20,Fsaid: "Increasing Council Tax by 8.5%
OL,21,Fwas not a decision taken lightly.
OL,26,@|D@GOU
