OL,3,CCouncil tax in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,4,Cto increase by 8.5%
OL,6,F"However, councillors decided that
OL,7,Fthis increase ` alongside required
OL,8,Fsavings ` is necessary to maintain the
OL,9,Fessential services and support our
OL,10,Fcouncil provides, across Dumfries and
OL,11,FGalloway, all while keeping our
OL,12,Ffinances on a sustainable footing."
